videos.description: Wisconsin's Micah Potter backs down a defender in the post, then quickly spins past him on the way to a jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Potter gets to the rim on sneaky spin move) 2020/02/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Potter gets to the rim on sneaky spin move

videos.description: Wisconsin's D'Mitrik Trice attacks the paint and slips past a defender for the tough layup plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Trice slips past defender for the and-1) 2020/02/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trice slips past defender for the and-1

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson slips behind Wisconsin's defense and muscles to the rim for the layup, putting an exclamation point on his 16-point first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Simspon closes big first half with tough layup) 2020/02/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simspon closes big first half with tough layup

videos.description: Wisconsin's Aleem Ford buries a 3-pointer and a pin drop can be heard amongst the Michigan faithful in the Crisler Center.
videos.headline: Ford's 3-pointer silences Michigan crowd
